🔴 EMERGENCY POST‼️
This post is to notify you all that recently someone has created a fake account using this foreign sim number (+971 58 130 5710) in  whatsapp using my pictures & videos. Also to make people believe that he/she is not fraud this person sending my Instagram id link to the people & making people confused. People are getting text from this fake id demanding money & offer for photoshoot. I am requesting you all that please don’t respond to those text & report that fake id Instantly. If you become a victim of that fake id then there’s nothing I could do for you. Also I will take multiple steps against that fake id including complaining to Cyber Crime unit of DMP,filing a GD, tracking IP address & many more.Whoever is the person behind that fake id, please refrain yourself from doing this heinous act. Otherwise you will face legal action from my side.
Thank you.
